    "The lowest accuracy score assigned to answers was 4, observed for 14.2% (n=2) questions.",
    "Additionally, the lowest completeness score, rated at 2, was attributed to 42.9% (n=6) of questions.Among the Google Bard AI answers, the median accuracy score was 5 (mean: 4.5, SD: 2.03) and the median completeness score was 2 (mean: 2.14, SD: 1.03).",
